1.1.1.1
log
@import p5-Tie-Cache-LRU-Expires

This is an expiring LRU cache, using Tie::Cache::LRU. Each entry
in this cache expires after 'EXPIRES' seconds (default 3600).
The cache is in RAM (see Tie::Cache::LRU).

ok merdely@@
